IMDB-Film
======================

IMDB::Film is OO Perl interface to the database of films
IMDB (www.imdb.com). It allows to retrieve information
about movies by its IMDB code or title. Also, there is a 
possibility to get information about IMDB persons (actors,
actresses, directors etc) by their name of code.

For more details please read POD of that module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   	perl Makefile.PL
   	make
   	make test
   	make install

To install this module in the specific path use:
	
	perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=/path/to/your/lib

To install the module in your home directory use that command:

	perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=YOU_HOME/path/to/your/lib

Note: you don't need to have a root privileges to do that!	

Also, you can use CPAN shell:

	> perl -MCPAN -e shell
	cpan> install IMDB::Film

or use command 'cpan':

	> cpan install IMDB::Film

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  	HTML::TokeParser
	LWP::Simple
    Cache::Cache	  

